1️⃣ What Happens When You Open a Website (Deep Interview Answer)
Simple Answer (What most students say ❌)

“DNS → HTTP → page loads”

👉 Not enough for interviews.

Perfect Answer (What interviewer wants ✅)
Step-by-step flow:
URL entered
DNS lookup → domain → IP
TCP 3-way handshake
TLS handshake (if HTTPS)
HTTP request sent (GET)
Routing via routers
Server processes request
Response sent back
Browser renders page
Mental Model 🧠

Like ordering food online:

search restaurant
connect
secure payment
place order
delivery
Why This Matters

👉 This is MOST ASKED QUESTION in placements.

2️⃣ TCP vs UDP (INTERVIEW TWIST)
Interview Trap Question

👉 “Which is better TCP or UDP?”

Smart Answer ✅

“Neither is universally better. It depends on use case.”

Example Answer
TCP → banking, email (reliable)
UDP → gaming, streaming (fast)
Why Interviewers Ask

To check:

conceptual clarity
real-world thinking
Memory Trick

Right tool for right job

