4️⃣ DNS vs ARP (Common Confusion)
Interview Question

👉 “Difference between DNS and ARP?”

Perfect Answer
DNS	ARP
Name → IP	IP → MAC
Works on internet	Works in LAN
Mental Model
DNS → find building
ARP → find exact room
Memory Trick

DNS → big level
ARP → local level

